title: April 2008 General Conference
description:
Twice a year, The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints holds a general conference of the Church.  The Prophet, Apostles, and other leaders of the Church give talks on the Gospel of Jesus Christ.

These are the MP3 files taken from http://www.lds.org for every talk from the April 2008 General Conference, excluding Priesthood Session.


For more info u can also visit http://www.mormon.org/mormonorg/eng/
